   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Leonard Cheshire Disability</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project proposes to work alongside ten inclusive primary schools, together with other service providers, community members and duty-bearers, to develop tools and systems for standardising educational assessments so that Ministries of Health and Education can implement inclusive strategies for education. The results of this work could be implemented with minimal investment in Kenya, and could be extended to non-disabled children, secondary education and informal education.</narrative>
  </description>
